Controls for this game:
Start Game: SPACE
Paddle up: CONTROL
Paddle down: SHIFT

poke 53280,0 - set border to black
poke 53281,0 - set background to black

printing "E" changes text color to white.
printing "S" puts the cursor in the upper left hand corner.
printing "heart (Control-S)" clears the screen.

peek 197 - examines the keyboard code. 60 is the spacebar.
peek 653 - checks status of shift keys. 4 is the control key.

1024-2023 is the default area for screen memory. Assuming a screen of (0,0) to (39,24), character at (x,y) is 1024 + y*40 + x.
